{"tid":13763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［樂視爆煲］18世盃轉播無香港份！","createTime":"2016-11-30T08:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:23:36.000Z","uid":785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca61e2ce57b23e7ac11ffbe14d184b328f76dd5d","tid":13763,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55983907 樂視爆煲後續？FIFA官方文件：2018年世界盃轉播無香港份！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55983907%20%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2%E5%BE%8C%E7%BA%8C%EF%BC%9FFIFA%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A2018%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E8%BD%89%E6%92%AD%E7%84%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%81&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=13865995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D55983907%20%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2%E5%BE%8C%E7%BA%8C%EF%BC%9FFIFA%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A2018%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E8%BD%89%E6%92%AD%E7%84%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%81&h=1f9a606c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=55983907 樂視爆煲後續？FIFA官方文件：2018年世界盃轉播無香港份！</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳出財困的樂視，曾經大肆宣傳已奪得2018年俄羅斯世界盃香港播放權，不過，據FIFA 2018年世界盃媒體轉播權最新文件（ <a href=\"http://fifa.to/2fAvFIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffifa.to%2F2fAvFIU&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2eb0f452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fifa.to/2fAvFIU</a> ），上面並無香港的名字！簡單而言，即是香港並無人奪得世界盃的獨家播放權！本報已向樂視查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\nFIFA官方文件列出全球132個地方，有哪一個媒體公司已獲得2018年俄羅斯世界盃播放權，包括電視、電台、移動媒體及網上媒體，但在亞洲之中，台灣、南韓等地榜上有名，但並沒有「香港」、甚至「中國」的名稱，顯示香港以至內地都沒有轉播俄羅斯世界盃的權利。<br />\n<br />\n樂視昨日傳出有意裁員10%救亡，大約涉及800員工，由手機部門擴展到汽車、體育等，實行N+1補償制度，非上市公司的子板塊已經開始著手處理。有報道指樂視體育原有的賽事運營板塊將會被逐漸砍掉，收縮戰線，專注做體育媒體。"},{"pid":"25c20b85dc2b77e86114d57e79f3bfd21f6861e4","tid":13763,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664b45024934e8c65e6f0b92ea2a2427fd147926","tid":13763,"uid":4082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b59b2a2136375461fac621509034b29b0a9d4e9","tid":13763,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"捉野牛牛有無過黎lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03566fa8f4d61c2f9fd394239e9e90f78c41f085","tid":13763,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉野牛牛有無過黎lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一定已經永續樂視啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}